:: Mansion Passout Pair
<<set $outside to 0>><<effects>>

<<generate1>><<person1>><<generate2>>
<<bind>>
<<facewear "blindfold">>
<<set $avery_mansion.assault_pair to 1>>

"Ah," says a <<personsimple>>'s voice. "Looks like <<pshes>> awake."
<br><br>
A blindfold covers your face, and you feel carpet beneath your back.
<br><br>
"This is our chance," says another voice. "Avery thinks <<nnpc_he Avery>>'s so high and mighty, but <<nnpc_his Avery>> <<girlfriend>> is ours now."
<br><br>

<<link [[Threaten to tell Avery about them|Mansion Passout Pair Threaten]]>><</link>>
<br>
<<if $demon gte 6>>
	<<link [[Goad them into untying your hands|Mansion Passout Pair Goad]]>><</link>><<demon>>
	<br>
<</if>>
<<link [[Remain silent|Mansion Passout Pair Silent]]>><</link>>
<br>


:: Mansion Passout Pair Threaten
<<effects>>

<<if $speech_attitude is "meek">>
	"Please don't do anything rash," you say. "I recognise your voices, and I'll tell Avery what you've done."
<<elseif $speech_attitude is "bratty">>
	"I know who you are," you say. "Avery will make you pay for this. If there's anything left when I'm done with you, that is."
<<else>>
	"I recognise your voices," you say. "Avery won't be pleased."
<</if>>
<br><br>

The <<person1>><<personsimple>> laughs. "We're skipping town after this. Fuck Avery, and fuck you."
<br>
"Good idea," the other voice says, reaching for you.
<br><br>

<<link [[Next|Mansion Passout Pair Rape]]>><<set $molestationstart to 1>><</link>>
<br>


:: Mansion Passout Pair Goad
<<effects>>

<<if $speech_attitude is "meek">>
	"You have me all to yourselves," you say. "Could you release my arms so I can serve you better?"
<<elseif $speech_attitude is "bratty">>
	"Taking Avery's <<girlfriend>> right under <<nnpc_his Avery>> Nose?" you say. "Delicious." You raise your arms. "Let me help."
<<else>>
	"This is a once in a lifetime opportunity for you," you say, raising your arms. "It would be a shame if you couldn't enjoy me fully."
<</if>>
<br><br>

Overcome by lust, trembling hands untie the rope binding your wrists together. You pull your blindfold up a little, for a peek. You're in one of Avery's spare rooms. There's a bed, but something large sits on it, covered by a white sheet. The door is on the other side.
<br><br>
<<unbind>>
The voices belong to a <<person1>><<person>> and <<person2>><<person>>. They watch you, eager, but waiting for you to make the next move.
<br><br>

<<if hasSexStat("promiscuity", 2)>>
	<<link [[Drain them|Mansion Passout Pair Sex]]>><<set $sexstart to 1>><</link>><<promiscuous2>>
	<br>
<</if>>
<<link [[Leave|Mansion Passout Pair Leave]]>><</link>>
<br>

:: Mansion Passout Pair Leave
<<effects>>

You smile at the pair, then walk away while pulling off the blindfold. You're halfway to the door before they realise you intend to leave.
<br><br>

"Wait!" the <<person1>><<person>> shouts, but it's too late. They're not so bold as to attack you in the hall outside.
<br><br>
<<set $worn.face.type.push("broken")>>
<<faceruined>>

<<link [[Next|Mansion Bedroom]]>><<endevent>><</link>>
<br>


