:: Mansion Passout Saved
<<set $outside to 0>><<effects>>

<<npc Avery>><<person1>>
You awaken in Avery's bedroom, on the mattress. Avery emerges from the bathroom, and flashes a smile.
<br><br>

"Were you too tired to make it to bed?" <<he>> asks. "I'm glad you're pushing yourself, but there are limits."
<br><br>

A thoughtful look flashes across <<his>> face, and <<he>> walks away.
<br><br>

<<link [[Next|Mansion Bedroom]]>><<endevent>><</link>>
<br>

:: Mansion Passout Ascended
<<set $outside to 0>><<effects>>

You awaken in darkness, arms floating beside you. The platform beneath wobbles as you rise. It's a raft. Still water stretches in all directions.
<br><br>

The water stirs. Bubbles rise to the surface, growing more intense, until the sea around you boils. A fell glow pulses into life, yet it illuminates nothing. You curl up, letting the raft shield you.
<br><br>

"You shouldn't be here." The voice is familiar. Distorted limbs rise from the water, followed by a head menacing with metal spikes. "Awaken."
<br><br>

Your eyes snap open. Avery's bed creaks beneath you.
<br><br>

<<link [[Next|Mansion Bedroom]]>><<endevent>><</link>>
<br>

:: Mansion Passout Rage
<<set $outside to 0>><<effects>>
<<npc Avery>><<person1>>
You awaken to a sharp sensation on your face. You're sat upright. Avery is gripping your shoulder, and staring at you.<<gpain>><<gstress>><<pain 4>><<stress 6>>
<br><br>

"I almost fucking tripped," <<he>> says. "You might be used to sleeping wherever like a fucking wild animal, but you will at least pretend to be civilised while you live with me. Understood?" <<He>> rises, and walks away.
<br><br>
<<endevent>>
<<avery_mansion_end_links>>

:: Mansion Passout Avery
<<set $outside to 0>><<effects>>

<<npc Avery>><<person1>>
You awaken as a force pulls you to a sitting position. Avery crouches in front of you, one eyebrow raised.
<br><br>

"An odd place to sleep," <<he>> says, rising to <<his>> feet. "Try to make it to the bed next time. I almost tripped over you." <<He>> walks away.
<br><br>
<<endevent>>
<<avery_mansion_end_links>>
